\"\u003e\n        committed \u003cspan class=\"discourse-local-date\" data-format=\"ll\" data-date=\"2021-11-12\" data-time=\"09:21:29\" data-timezone=\"UTC\"\u003e09:21AM - 12 Nov 21 UTC\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"user\"\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/slouken\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"\u003e\n          \u003cimg alt=\"slouken\" src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2100061?v=4\" class=\"onebox-avatar-inline\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"\u003e\n          slouken\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"lines\" title=\"changed 2 files with 8 additions and 1 deletions\"\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL/commit/97c71371f21187f146872d41f94a5593c0a374ba\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"\u003e\n          \u003cspan class=\"added\"\u003e+8\u003c/span\u003e\n          \u003cspan class=\"removed\"\u003e-1\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"github-row\"\u003e\n    \u003cp class=\"github-body-container\"\u003e\"If your app targets Android 12, you must specify the mutability of each Pending\u003cspan class=\"show-more-container\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL/commit/97c71371f21187f146872d41f94a5593c0a374ba\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" class=\"show-more\"\u003e‚Ä¶\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"excerpt hidden\"\u003eIntent object that your app creates. This additional requirement improves your app's security.\"\n\nThanks @FormularSumo and @cgutman\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/article\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"onebox-metadata\"\u003e\n    \n    \n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv style=\"clear: both\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor now I downgraded my targetSdkVersion to 30 